    "Preprocessing involves data normalization and cleansing.",
    "The preprocessed data is then used to recover characteristics such as \"Weighted Geometric Mean Principal Component Analysis (WGM-PCA), statistical features, higherorder statistical features, and weighted modified correlation-based features.\"",
    "The most pertinent attributes are selected using the Improved Attribute Ranker (IAR).",
    "Additionally, a deep learning model based on an ensemble of classifiers that includes optimized \"Bi-GRU, Multi-Layer Perceptron (MLP), and Quantum Neural Network (QDNN)\" represents the disease categorization phase.",
